menu "breadboard: bb_power_routes"

config BB_POWER_ROUTES_AUTOREGISTER
    bool "Auto-register /api/power HTTP route via bb_init"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, bb_power_routes self-registers GET /api/power through
        bb_init at order 1 (after order-0 satellites have registered
        their extenders). Disable to call bb_power_routes_init manually.
        This is opt-in (default off) to prevent polluting consumers that define
        their own /api/power handler or don't have the hardware. Enable this
        config (or call bb_power_routes_init) when your app wants BB to own
        the route.

endmenu
